| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1924 — Recovery Inhibition (payoutsking)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: b68457fa-ea56-5647-83e6-bbe37b2bf0f2"
